name: Monstercat
description:
The mascot from the canadian music label Monstercat.
The tricolored bandana represents the three imprints of the record label: Monstercat Instinct, represented by green; Monstercat Uncaged, represented by purple; and Monstercat Silk, represented by yellow.

The yellow color of the bandana was originally orange but was changed to yellow because of the French flag's red color being similar to the color orange.

This pixelart was originally created by Flufmuni from the Monstercat discord server but it was resized and shaded by ItsAceNotHerobrineAS.

And this pixelart is part of the Furry_IRL alliance.
